Former X-Men Director and Producer Simon Kinberg has been spotted inside Hall H!

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/e1bc49cc-c676-43a4-abc2-ad2fc22514b1/20240727_180500.jpg?format=original)

Fans have noticed Marvel Studios set up a Young Avengers Instagram account just prior to the Hall H presentation

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/4c4d1b6a-0b1a-4e9f-8c57-26b28ebb0f83/20240727_180921.jpg?format=original)

The Marvel panel kicks off to a cheering crowd with the opening logo from Deadpool and Wolverine - and now a musical performance of Like A Prayer

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/1b409fed-1953-495b-bd34-cb67d3a78237/20240727_181252.jpg?format=original)

Kevin Feige announced that just moments ago, Deadpool and Wolverine became the highest grossing R Rated opening night OF ALL TIME

📷: @ErikDavis

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/7d9ec8c7-8fa6-42f4-92c7-a1b7b650d45d/20240727_181638.jpg?format=original)

Kevin Feige says the Marvel Studios Hall H panel will only focus on 3 movies. We start with Captain America: Brave New World

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/3185e9b3-67f9-4a22-952f-51c856f17fe6/20240727_181847.jpg?format=original)

\-Giancarlo Esposito is officially playing Sidewinder in Captain America Brave New World!

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/8aad4c61-2d4d-4a01-9839-30e87ab1d9ce/20240727_182205.jpg?format=original)

* * *

A scene from Captain America Brave New World is being shown to the audience

The clip from confirms the MCU version of Adamantium comes from Celestials.

The clip shows Harrison Ford’s Thaddeus Ross talking about the Celestial coming out of Earth confirming Tiamut is the source of the metal

Ross reportedly turns into Red Hulk in front of the White House during a speech in ‘CAPTAIN AMERICA BRAVE NEW WORLD’, in a scene shown at Marvel Studios’ SDCC Hall H Panel.

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/afd60c53-1696-480e-9bda-ec1927fc88e3/20240727_183040.jpg?format=original)

It's time for the THUNDERBOLTS\* panel. David Harbor arrives in full costume.

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/cde42766-00b0-4c11-baea-2e08791827e6/20240727_183400.jpg?format=original)

Kevin Feige is asked what does the asterisks mean in the Thunderbolts title. He won't tell. Feige says you'll have to see the movie.

Sebastian Stan says Florence Pugh is the standout of this film. An exclusive clip is shown to the crowd.

Thunderbolts\* is being described as being unhinged and gritty. “There are bad guys, and there are BAD guys is a tagline for the film.

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/09fe2562-a2ea-4387-ac25-989cee6a14f6/20240727_184518.jpg?format=original)

Matt Shankman joins the stage as the panel begins to focus on Fantastic Four

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/377bf118-f8bf-4d1a-93a1-7987930e1560/20240727_185102.jpg?format=original)

‘THE FANTASTIC FOUR: FIRST STEPS’ is the official title of the MCU's first ever F4 film.

‘FANTASTIC FOUR’ is described as set in a “retro future of the ‘60s”

Matt Shakman says they went to the desert to find the best type of rock to make The Thing out of

Pre-shoot material of ‘FANTASTIC FOUR’ is being shown, shot in 4:3

Pedro Pascal has an old school accent as Reed Richards, teaching a science class.

Concept art is shown of the futuristic yet 1960s retro world of the F4. The Fantasticar is an old Cadillac that looks straight out of ‘The Jetsons’

Michael Giacchino will compose the score for ‘FANTASTIC FOUR’

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/a111ef75-f45f-4f4a-9f9b-9972b8506deb/20240727_185333.jpg?format=original)

The cast takes the stage and we get a look at our new First Family

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/a7ca45a2-34ec-4c35-86ce-4dc8dccc70c1/20240727_185302.jpg?format=original)

Early footage of Galactus in ‘FANTASTIC FOUR’ showed his face peering through a building, very clearly a giant cosmic entity.

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/d0f5fb03-cc8e-4d96-89ee-30c069d4dbdf/20240727_185829.jpg?format=original)

The Fantastic Four ARE CONFIRMED to appear in both upcoming ‘AVENGERS’ films

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/448448af-70c9-448f-a067-52e3b4b95e62/20240727_190610.jpg?format=original)

ROBERT DOWNEY JR HAS RETURNED TO THE MCU AS DOCTOR DOOM!!!

DR. DOOM HAS ARRIVED IN THE MCU.

AVENGERS 5 IS NOW TITLED AVENGERS: DOOMSDAY!!!!!

* * *

